        {
            "title": "Infosys季度營收超預期 預測2027財年增長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0x9mOd200zuNQg8NRqf3jQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEDB10AU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 印度IT巨頭Infosys週四公佈的季度營收超出分析師預期,受惠於銀行、能源和通訊板塊需求增加。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司截至3月的三個月營收為4,640.2億盧比,超過分析師平均預估的4,603億盧比。營收較去年同期增長13.4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該季度淨利潤達到850.1億盧比,超過分析師預估的746.5億盧比。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">展望2027財年,<span><span>Infosys</span></span>預測營收增長為1.5%至3.5%,低於券商預估的全年2%至4%。該公司預測本財年營運利潤率為20%至22%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6236b3e9-fe07-357d-8076-aae1b004e2fb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Infosys宣佈每股股息為25盧比。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家IT服務公司還宣佈在日本成立一家間接全資子公司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/infosys%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E8%B6%85%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC2027%E8%B2%A1%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7-124936442.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 21:15:25",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Super Micro因傳失去甲骨文14億美元合約而暴跌10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6_CrUd2j8qGyL_GQv5r0.g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7I0CN_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <span>Super Micro Computer</span> (NASDAQ:SMCI)股價週四下跌10%,此前有報導稱該公司失去了與甲骨文(NYSE:ORCL)簽訂的英偉達(NASDAQ:NVDA)GB300 NVL72機架的重大合約。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Bluefin\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Bluefin;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Bluefin\">Bluefin</a>研究報告,<span><span>甲骨文</span></span>從<span><span><span><span>Super Micro</span></span> Computer</span></span>取消了300至400個機架的訂單,每個機架價值約350萬美元,總合約損失金額達11億至14億美元。該公司估計,Super Micro Computer在訂單取消前已出貨100至200個機架。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a23560e8-af39-3c91-86ac-87c6d9587a71-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bluefin引述的業界消息人士指出,甲骨文取消訂單據信與Super Micro Computer聯合創始人因走私AI GPU至中國而被起訴有關。據該研究報告稱,緯穎科技據信已接手該機架業務。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bluefin還指出,Super Micro Computer的xAI業務在今年稍早完成Colossus 2數據中心的GB300機架出貨後已經放緩,而Rubin的推出仍需數月時間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司對Super Micro Computer的B200 GPU庫存過剩提出了額外擔憂。據Bluefin稱,供應鏈消息人士將庫存水平形容為\"相當可觀\"。該公司原本為xAI HGX AI伺服器出貨而累積了B200庫存,但當機架出貨在2025年年中加速時,xAI的需求轉向了GB200 NVL72。這些機架被授予戴爾(NYSE:DELL)和惠普企業(NYSE:HPE)。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Bluefin研究報告,Super Micro Computer後來在2025年下半年獲得了xAI的GB300 NVL72機架訂單,但一直無法消化較舊的B200庫存。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/super-micro%E5%9B%A0%E5%82%B3%E5%A4%B1%E5%8E%BB%E7%94%B2%E9%AA%A8%E6%96%8714%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E8%80%8C%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C10-123305747.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 21:15:27",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
